Name: Intake Note Psychiatry - Ambrose
ServerSideScript:
Class FormScriptEvents

private sub OnSave()
    if theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare") <> "" then
        theForm.FormGroupName=theForm.execScalerSQL("select  __FormGroupName from ct_Chart_EpisodeOfCare where __FormInstanceGUID =  '" & theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare")  & "'")
        theForm.FormGroupFolder=theForm.execScalerSQL("select __FormGroupFolder from ct_Chart_EpisodeOfCare where __FormInstanceGUID =  '" & theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare")  & "'")

        theForm.execScalerSQL("exec cstm_UpdateAppointmentHeaderRecord @NewCalGUID = '" & theForm("cmbSession") & "', @OldCalGUID = '" & theForm("txtPreviousCalUID") & "', @formGUID = '" & theForm("__forminstanceguid").toString & "' ")                
        theForm.execScalerSQL("exec cstm_UpdateAppointmentHeaderRecordEOC @NewCalGUID = '" & theForm("cmbSession") & "', @OldCalGUID = '" & theForm("txtPreviousCalUID") & "', @EOC = '" & theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare") & "' ")
        theForm("txtPreviousCalUID") = theForm("cmbSession")
    end if

    'Edit Diagnosis and Portal Assignments buttons
    editInstanceGuid = System.String.Format("select Cast(__FormInstanceGUID as varchar(36)) from [ct_Chart_Edit_Diagnosis] where __FormGroupFolder = (select __FormGroupFolder from ct_Chart_EpisodeOfCare where __FormInstanceGUID =  '{0}' )", theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare"))
    portalInstanceGuid = System.String.Format("select Cast(__FormInstanceGUID as varchar(36)) from [ct_Chart_Form Assignment] where __ownerobjectguid = '{0}'", theForm.DataStore.OwnerObjectGUID.tostring)
    theForm("editInstanceGuid") = theForm.execScalerSQL(editInstanceGuid)
    theForm("portalInstanceGuid") = theForm.execScalerSQL(portalInstanceGuid)
end sub
private sub OnCreate()
    theForm("cmbSession") = theForm.GetUrlParameterValue("CalendarGUID") 

    dim tempSQL
    tempSQL = "select Cast(__FormInstanceGUID as varchar(36)) from [dbo].[ct_Chart_EpisodeOfCare] where __formgroupfolder = (select top(1) Cast(FormGroupID as varchar(36)) from vClient where vClient.vCalItemGuid = '{0}' and vClient.ContactGuid = '{1}')"
    FormGroupFolder = theForm.execScalerSQL(System.String.Format(tempSQL, theForm.GetUrlParameterValue("CalendarGUID"), theForm.Datastore.OwnerObjectGuid.tostring))
    theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare") = FormGroupFolder
    
    'theForm("txtEpisodeOfCare") = theForm.execScalerSQL("exec [cstm__getEOCs] @ContactGUID = '" & theForm.DataStore.OwnerObjectGUID.ToString & "' , @TreatmentModality = 'Psychiatry'")
    Pop()
end sub
private sub OnLoad()
    Pop()
    ' GetLockState()
end sub

private sub OnAfterSave()
    Pop()
    ' GetLockState()
     dim NameDate 
    NameDate = theForm.execScalerSQL("select Cast(format(dbo.ToLocalTime(dtstart), 'yyyy/MM/dd') as varchar(10)) from vCalendar where vCalendar.uid = '" & theForm("cmbSession") & "'")
    
    theForm("chkFinalSignOff") = theForm.execScalerSQL("SELECT chkFinalSignOff FROM [ct_Intake and Progress Notes_Session_Documentation_SignOff] WHERE txtParentInstanceGUID = '" & theForm.FormInstanceGUID.ToString & "'")
    
    theForm("__instancename") = "Intake Note - " & NameDate & " - " ' Should be start Date of session
    if theForm("chkFinalSignOff") = true Then
        theForm("__instancename") = theForm("__instancename") & "Signed Off"
    elseif theForm("__locked") = true Then
        theForm("__instancename") = theForm("__instancename") & "Pending Supervisor Sign Off"
    else
        theForm("__instancename") = theForm("__instancename") & "Unsigned"
    end if

    theForm.execScalerSQL("UPDATE [ct_Intake and Progress Notes_Intake_Psychiatry_Ambrose] SET __instancename = '" & theForm("__instancename") & "' WHERE __forminstanceguid = '" & theForm.FormInstanceGUID.ToString & "'")
    theForm.execScalerSQL("UPDATE Header SET [Subject] = '" & theForm("__instancename") & "' WHERE HeaderGUID = '" & theForm.FormInstanceGUID.ToString & "'")
end sub
private sub Pop()
        theForm("HiddenUsername") = theForm.user.fullname
        theForm("HiddenUserguid") = theForm.user.contactguid.tostring
        profDesSQL = "exec [cstm_getProfDes] @ContactGUID = '" & theForm.user.contactguid.tostring & "'"
        theForm("hiddenProfDes") = theForm.execScalerSQL(profDesSQL)
end sub
private sub GetLockState()
    sql = "SELECT chkSignedOff FROM [ct_Intake and Progress Notes_Session_Documentation_SignOff] so JOIN [dbo].[ct_Intake and Progress Notes_ParentForm_relation_Session Documentation SignOff] rel ON so.__forminstanceguid = rel.referenceForm WHERE so.txtParentInstanceGUID = '" & theForm.FormInstanceGUID.tostring & "'"
    IsLocked = theForm.execScalerSQL(sql)
    
    If IsLocked = "True" then
        theForm("__locked") = True
    else 
        theForm("__locked") = False
    End if    
end sub
End Class
